Martin Lewis (English actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Martin_Lewis_(English_actor) 0 Martin Lewis, (born 8 September 1888 in Blackheath, Kent – died 1 April 1970 in Farnborough Common, Orpington, Kent), was an English actor. He has appeared in various films and shows including The Stronger Sex, The Riverside Murder, The Heirloom Mystery and the series Emergency-Ward 10.
